Plot predictions for GAMs over time, by season

show_prdseason.Rd

Plot predictions for GAMs over time, by season

show_prdseason(moddat = NULL, mods = NULL, ylab, nfac = NULL, ...)

Arguments

moddat

input raw data, one station and parameter
mods

optional list of model objects
ylab

chr string for y-axis label
nfac

numeric indicating column number for facets, passed to ncol argument of facet_wrap, defaults to one
...

additional arguments passed to other methods

Value

A ggplot object

See also

Other show: show_avgseason, show_perchg, show_prd3d, show_prddoy, show_prdseries

Examples

library(dplyr)

# get predictions for all four gams
tomod <- rawdat %>%
  filter(station %in% 32) %>%
  filter(param %in% 'chl')
if (FALSE) {
show_prdseason(moddat = tomod, ylab = 'Chlorophyll-a (ug/L)', trans = 'boxcox')
}
# use previously fitted list of models
trans <- 'boxcox'
mods <- list(
  gam0 = anlz_gam(tomod, mod = 'gam0', trans = trans),
  gam1 = anlz_gam(tomod, mod = 'gam1', trans = trans),
  gam2 = anlz_gam(tomod, mod = 'gam2', trans = trans)
)

show_prdseason(moddat = tomod, mods = mods, ylab = 'Chlorophyll-a (ug/L)')
